Definition: at right angles to the plane of the horizon or a base line
Example: a vertical camera angle; the monument consists of two vertical pillars supporting a horizontal slab; measure the perpendicular height
Synonyms: noun, relation, vertical, artifact, attribute, verticalness, verticality, INCLINED, HORIZONTAL, perpendicular, perpendicularity, STEEP, STRAIGHT, orientation, at, right, angles, to, the, plane, of, horizon, or, a, base, line, camera, angle, monument, consists, two, pillars, supporting, horizontal, slab, measure, height
Category: adj.all
